{"word":"ἐπιβαρέω","slug":"ἐπιβαρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιβαρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάρος\">βάρος</a></el>] ‘be burdensome to’, <b>burden, weigh down <a href='B:590 2:9'>1 Th 2:9</a>; <a href='B:600 3:8'>2 Th 3:8</a>.</b> In <b><a href='B:540 2:5'>2 Cor 2:5</a></b> <el>ἱνα <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μὴ\">μὴ</a> ἐπιβαρῶ</el> appears to be idiomatic for to put it gently. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιβαλῶ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιβάς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}